#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another picture of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Enter your gmail."
"com address and click <guibutton>&nbsp;Next&nbsp;</guibutton>. You will be "
"asked to enter your gmail password."
msgstr ""
